flowchart LR
    ST["Schedule Trigger
    (every hour)"]
    RSS1["RSS Feed Read
    (blog.n8n.io)"]
    RSS2["RSS Feed Read
    (blog.python.org)"]
    EC["Execute Command
    (mkdir /tmp/workflow7)"]
    MG["Merge
    (Append)"]
    CODE["Code: filter by keyword
    (Python / JS)"]
    CVT["Convert to/from File
    (JSON)"]
    WF["Write File to Disk
    (last_run.json)"]
    TG["Telegram: Send Message
    (article summary)"]

    ST --> RSS1 --> MG
    ST --> RSS2 --> MG
    ST --> EC --> MG
    MG --> CODE --> CVT --> WF --> TG
